reviews.review_text:
Even If You're Already Up Part 2 This show will place and leave a perpetual smile on your face. 

Live in the moment and listen to a magnificent show and recording/remastering from 30 years ago.

This one bears the Evan S. Hunt seal of approval.

Happy Fathers Day to you all and a merry summer solstice.

Part2 20Jun80 Just as good the second time around.
What a truly amazing performance! 

48 out of 5 stars.
